{
  "id": "RAW_2d34e6f8",
  "title": "扣子 2.0，让 Agent 更进一步",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MzYzMjE0MQ==&mid=2247517978&idx=1&sn=f84abb409d081bcff9aa0fd841631303",
  "date": "2026-01-19 09:29:00",
  "author": "字节跳动技术团队",
  "siteName": "字节跳动技术团队",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260123064857_126a027.jpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:2px;font-size:14px;line-height:2.2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2024年2月1日，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;\">「扣子」</span>第一次和你见面。我们怀着对 AI 能力的憧憬，在扣子里不断拖拽工作流节点、反复优化提示词，只为真的能把活儿交给AI。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025年4月20日，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;\">「扣子空间」</span>诞生了。那时候的它还很青涩，只会帮你做做总结，画画网页。你问一句，它答一句，像个随叫随到但不太会来事儿的实习生。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;\">直到今天，扣子已经陪你走过了七百多个日夜，拥有了上千万的用户。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">上千万的扣子用户背后，是千万个具体的人：有人在通勤的地铁上，用扣子赶完了周报；有人在孩子睡着后，用扣子偷偷改完了PPT；有人通过扣子写的网页，拿下大客户；也有人，在用过扣子后第一次感受到，“原来我也能做出这么酷炫的东西”……</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些故事里，都有同一种心声：“多亏有扣子帮把手” 。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;\">但我们发现，你需要的远不止“帮把手”。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">一份周报的背后，是从立项、执行到总结的长期链路；一个网页的上线，是从想法到部署的完整过程。你更想问的是：\"扣子，能不能从头到尾，把这件事搞定？\"</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">你需要的，不是一个只会回答问题的工具，而是一个能主动推进、持续执行的靠谱伙伴。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;\">扣子2.0 ，就从这里开始。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.17405266538214514\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1557\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/6Qibp6lbmicKXBn0OO8oLYdKm00ylBPRYgj1HlmPJEneK0Ev5kYB4OibbPuibwr5tF2yRX1uwDQqGbjWZ84xs2pctg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"548\" data-cropsely2=\"98\" data-imgfileid=\"100004127\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260123064857_f916d42.png\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;color: rgb(96, 73, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent Skills 是什么？</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 知道怎么写代码、写文案、做PPT，但它不知道怎么把代码写得规范、写出有销售力的文案、设计出好看的排版。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">因为后者需要的不是知识，而是经验。每份工作都有独特的职业技巧，只有真正“懂行”的人才能熟练上手，才能总结出来最佳实践。如果我们能把这些经验，变成每个人都可以直接调用的能力呢？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">——这个转化，就是技能（Agent Skills）。</span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个 Agent Skill，本质上是</span><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">「场景最佳实践 + 所需工具」</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">的封装。比如一个“营销文案写作”Skill，可能包含：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"color:#6049fd;font-weight:bold;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2.2;padding: 0px 15px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;list&quot;,{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;ul&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;list-style-type: disc;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;list-paddingleft-1&quot;,&quot;start&quot;:null},&quot;listitem&quot;,{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color:#6049fd;font-weight:bold;&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">成功的营销文案框架（比如AIDA模型、痛点共鸣模型）</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"color:#6049fd;font-weight:bold;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;\">调研工具（去哪里找目标用户的话术）</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"color:#6049fd;font-weight:bold;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;\">写作技巧（怎么用数据和案例增强说服力）</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"color:#6049fd;font-weight:bold;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;\">质量检查（如何避免常见误区）</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">当你给 AI 安装这个 Skill 后，你的 AI 将不只是“写文案”，而是“写出能转化订单的文案”。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.8px;font-size:15px;line-height:2.2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">添加你的 Coze Skills，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.8px;font-size:15px;line-height:2.2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">像给扣子装了一个</span><span style=\"line-height: 2.2;font-style: normal;text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">「技能」系统</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.8px;font-size:15px;line-height:2.2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">你想让扣子成为什么领域的专家，就给扣子装什么技能。</span></p>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;color: rgb(96, 73, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如何找到合适的 Agent Skills？&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">每个人都可以通过</span><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">「扣子编程」</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">创建自己的 Skill：HR可以把面试技巧封装成“人才筛选” Skill，产品经理可以把需求分析方法封装成“需求挖掘” Skill……各行各业都有独特的 Skill。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">每个人都有自己的独门绝活，但如何让这些经验真正流动起来，帮助更多有需要的人？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">——扣子</span><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">「技能商店」</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">应运而生。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5601852\" data-s=\"300,640\" width=\"100%\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260123064857_4cdb5cc.png\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;color: rgb(96, 73, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">视频创作 Skill：言出法随，音画同步</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了让大家有更好的创作体验，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">扣子官方视频 Skill 今天也正式上线了。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">无需安装，你只需要用自然语言描述需求：“帮我做一个新春庙会的国风动画视频，要3D卡通风格，有书生、花旦、留学生等角色，还要有河南话、粤语、普通话和英语的台词，最后以烟花收尾……”即可自动使用视频创作 Skill。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">视频 Skill 会自动生成视频脚本、匹配视觉素材、完成剪辑和转场、配上音乐，调整节奏，一个视频就这样诞生了。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0.8px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多人在使用 AI 视频工具时会有这种感觉：画面和音频是割裂的，该快时画面在慢动作，该慢时画面在飞驰。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">但扣子视频 Skill 的音画同步做得非常丝滑，画面动态会精确匹配音频的节奏和波形——音乐高潮时画面冲击力强，对话时画面平稳，停顿处画面也在“呼吸”。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/6Qibp6lbmicKXBn0OO8oLYdKm00ylBPRYgAm2S7rJWPCPSvWqQMhP6OiaRebEJjaqMEZpMG3Kl4J3RicswY8rlufIA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"548\" data-cropsely2=\"96\" data-imgfileid=\"100004128\" data-ratio=\"0.17405266538214514\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1557\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260123064857_d9a47b4.png\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在用 AI 还是一种“主动提问”的模式？你需要主动问问题，AI 才回答。如果你想让它帮你做个长期项目，你得时不时提醒它该做什么。这不像工作伙伴，而是在使用一个坐等指令的工具。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么，可以反过来么？只需给 AI 一个长期目标，它自己规划执行路径，定期给你汇报进展。不用你追着问，它会主动找你。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">——这就是扣子新推出的</span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 78, 213);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">长期计划（Agent Plan）。</span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260123064857_a5c7719.png\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">举个例子，你想运营自媒体账号，只需要告诉扣子：“我想做个自媒体账号，帮我快速涨粉10w。”Agent 会自己执行：</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n   <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#fe4ed5;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(254, 78, 213);font-weight: bold;\">调查市场情况，明晰账号定位</span></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#fe4ed5;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(254, 78, 213);font-weight: bold;\">拆解每个阶段的运营策略</span></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#fe4ed5;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(254, 78, 213);font-weight: bold;\">每周自动创作内容</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"font-weight:bold;color:#fe4ed5;\">\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(254, 78, 213);font-weight: bold;\">监控数据，根据反馈调整内容策略</span></span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p></p>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">整个过程，你只需设一次目标，扣子 Agent 会持续几天甚至几个月来执行，直到完成你的目标。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.17405266538214514\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1557\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/6Qibp6lbmicKXBn0OO8oLYdKm00ylBPRYgsFa24k0n2PZGB3Pxic8ACq3vgGlibu7slm7KzEIvJmgMQdOore1zByfg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"548\" data-cropsely2=\"95\" data-imgfileid=\"100004129\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260123064857_d478ac5.png\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">向AI提问，目前获得的通常是标准答案，但真实的职场问题从来不会这么简单。AI 只有理解具体场景，才能提供针对性解决方案。扣子2.0在处理这类复杂职场问题上，做了两个升级。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;\">1.深度上下文理解。</span>你不需要一次性把所有背景信息塞进去，扣子会通过多轮对话，逐步理解具体情况。数据库架构、业务约束、性能目标……它会在对话中主动询问、确认。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;\">2.提供洞察，不只是答案。</span>这可能是对职场人最关键的一点</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如你问：“为什么订单转化率下降了5%”，标准AI可能会给提供几个排查方法，但扣子会先搞清楚具体情况，从战略层面分析背后原因。少一点漂亮的场面话，多一些核心的真痛点，仿佛咨询一个资深的职场前辈，不仅给你答案，还会告诉你背后的逻辑和经验。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种深度分析的能力，在各类复杂 Office 文档中同样适用。扣子擅长处理庞杂任务，写战略报告 Word、做分析PPT、梳理数据 Excel，你在工作中的任何所需，都可以交给扣子。5分钟，即可来一份拿得出手的材料。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/6Qibp6lbmicKXBn0OO8oLYdKm00ylBPRYgLJiaia4EHVicCsJZYBIQzvFVcT2G78OXBhoodZGpqanh3zHFqbGiat2hrw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"548\" data-cropsely2=\"68\" data-imgfileid=\"100004130\" data-ratio=\"0.17405266538214514\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1557\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260123064857_cfaca56.png\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">扣子开发平台，已经升级为扣子编程。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">扣子编程是一款一站式云端 Vibe Coding 开发平台。开箱即用，通过连续对话，即可轻松构建智能体、工作流、网站、移动应用等，并提供 Vibe Infra 基础设施，实现一键部署上线。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">从12月扣子编程开启免费公测以来，有用户开发了多人在线实际运行的游戏，有用户拿下了自己的定制化需求客户，也有非研发背景的用户开发出了复杂网站。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">无论你是专业开发者，还是小白用户，扣子编程都能满足你的需求。来扣子编程，实现你的创意吧！</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/6Qibp6lbmicKXBn0OO8oLYdKm00ylBPRYgNQYOibTZwEicpxC2ogqmjg5gDgYGibT27mVL1VLtJicgqjR98vOk8PZ0ZA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"548\" data-cropsely2=\"75\" data-imgfileid=\"100004131\" data-ratio=\"0.17405266538214514\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1557\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260123064857_438395e.png\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent Skills、Agent Plan、Agent Coding、Agent Office……随着这些能力的增强，「扣子空间」也正式升级为「扣子」2.0 。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">扣子 2.0 也会更好地传达它的定位和使命：帮助更多的职场人。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">HR还在手动筛选简历？有人用扣子3分钟筛选出Top 10；</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">市场人还在死磕文案？有人用扣子一键生成10条种草笔记；</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">销售人还在凭感觉跟进客户？有人用扣子自动分析痛点并生成话术；</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">财务人还在Excel里复制粘贴？有人用扣子拖拽数据直接生成分析报表；</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这不是别人，是扣子已经帮过的1000+万职场人。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在，扣子2.0来了：</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Agent Skills：</span>给扣子装上行业技能包，让通用AI变得更专业；</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Agent Plan：</span>你定目标，扣子持续执行并主动汇报；</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Agent Office：</span>深度理解职场场景，不止答案，更有洞察；</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Agent Coding：</span>从想法到上线，云端开发从未如此简单；</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">从能帮你，到懂你，扣子2.0，让 Agent 更进一步。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">靠谱工作伙伴，待你认领！</span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.8px;font-size:15px;line-height:2.2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">PC 访问</span><span leaf=\"\">Coze.cn，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.8px;font-size:15px;line-height:2.2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">或前往应用商店下载</span><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">「扣子」</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.8px;font-size:15px;line-height:2.2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">App，让扣子随时帮你搞定工作！</span></p>\n    <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-eleid=\"6216390\" style=\"line-height: 2.2;font-style: normal;text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(96, 73, 253);font-weight: bold;box-sizing: border-box;\">新用户登录，送5000积分；</span></span></p>\n    <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-eleid=\"31870818\" style=\"font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.8px;font-size:15px;line-height:2.2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(254, 78, 213);font-weight: bold;\">老用户升级，送100000积分；</span></span></span></p>\n    <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span data-eleid=\"77271057\"><span leaf=\"\">每日登录、邀请好友更有多重奖励，快来体验吧！</span></span></p>\n    <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.8px;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span data-eleid=\"77271057\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.4203703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260123064856_11156ee.png\"></span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 16px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkkpcr0ugsx\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkkpcpiguaw\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkkpcr0b1cpz\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.8px;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:0px;outline:0px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;max-width:100%;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">点击</span><strong style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.8px;text-decoration:none;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word